    <description>Naki bodies contain high amounts of exotic heavy particles. Heavy atoms allow Naki to live outside of Omega Eden, but make them reliable on daily ingestion or meditation.
\nWithout dark matter, Naki cannot heal and cast psycasts.</description>
    <hediffClass>Hediff_Addiction</hediffClass>
    <causesNeed>NakiRaceDMNeed</causesNeed>
    <everCurableByItem>false</everCurableByItem>
